-- LeBron James to Sign With Miami Heat, Leave Cleveland
-- Rob Gloster
-- 2010-07-09T01:27:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/lebron-james-to-sign-with-miami-heat-leave-cleveland.html

          
          
             LeBron James said in a nationally
televised show that he will move to the Miami Heat, joining
fellow All-Stars Dwyane Wade and Chris Bosh, leaving Cleveland
after seven National Basketball Association seasons with the
Cavaliers.  
          
          


  


        